Maintainer: Vincent Runge <vincent.runge@univ-evry.fr>
Description: Implements model-free screening procedures for selecting explanatory variables correlated with a response variable in high-dimensional settings. The package provides functions to compute marginal screening scores and screening tests based on studentized slope estimators, with false positive rate control.
